{
  "stem": "16503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 336.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there from about two, three weeks after we arrived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I stayed in Theresienstadt till-- and in that particular place till October '44.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Free contact with my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister followed us on her own in a different transport to Theresienstadt in three months later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father then came in another three months by himself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the whole family had-- we were living in different quarters, but we had a daily contact.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the evening, we would meet or sit on a bench and, and eat mush together or go to mother's crowded quarters and eat the mush there, or you know, stuff like this.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No we were in absolute contact at all times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The morale was-- well, I cannot speak for the grownups.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew that the war now was raging in, in Europe, that the British were in and the French were in and that was about all I can identify with.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that people were doing underground things in Theresienstadt and got shot for it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do not know them personally, but I knew of the-- of the happenings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew that the SS had a Kommandatur in Theres-- in the-- in the-- on the square.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The SS in Theresienstadt was not very visible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, they were not very visible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was a awful lot of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] politics going on in the grown up world, but I was not in the grown up world.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the-- in my world, we were continuing with sharing what we had or didn't have.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were close knit, very close knit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, as there was that boy-- girls' children's building, then there and there was a boys' building.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
